- OpenCL synchronization syscalls and cross-platform GPU barrier operations with work group synchronization
- OpenCL command queue management syscalls and cross-platform GPU execution queues with asynchronous execution
- OpenCL event management syscalls and cross-platform GPU timing operations with performance monitoring
